//*********************************************************************************************************	
//	START THE LOOP - IN THIS LOOP THE FOLLOWING WILL HAPPEN:
//	1. OPEN THE SelectGetCompanyNamesQueryOutput.txt FILE
//	2. ASK TO CONTINUE RUNNING AGAINST THE COMPANY
//	3. BACKUP THE DATABASE & THEN CHECK THAT IT HAS BACKED UP
//	4. CREATE THE companies.csv & WRITE THE LINE TO IT FOR MULTIDB UPDATER
//	5. RUN DBUPDATER
//	6. UPDATE FARM DATABSE TO COMPANIES NEW VERSION NUMBER
//	7. COPY THE PROHIRE CLIENT TO THE COMPANIES PROHIREFILES FOLDER
//	8. RESTART THE FILE SERVER
//	9. CREATE THE ProhireWindow.txt THAT HAS THAT COMPANIES PIN IN & COPY TO THEIR PROHIREFILES FOLDER
//  10. UPDATE THE FARM DATABASE TO COMPANIES NEW VERSION NUMBER 
